31	/// E.g., a slow subscriber could block the underlying Zenoh thread because it is not emptying the
32	/// [`FifoChannel`] fast enough. In this case, you may want to look into [`handlers::RingChannel`](crate::api::handlers::RingChannel) that
33	/// will drop samples when full.
